A fast, lightweight, terminal-based tool for sending HTTP requests to your local API during backend development â€” built entirely with Python.

This tool is designed to be simple, elegant, and fast â€” without the heavy UI of Postman or Hoppscotch.
Perfect for developers who love working inside the terminal.

